<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1" pageEncoding="ISO-8859-1"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="ISO-8859-1">
<title>About Us</title>
<style>
    /* Simple Styles for About Us Section */
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
    }

    .about-us-container {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        color: #004346;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #1ab2b2;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        color: #555;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="about-us-container">
    <h1>Welcome to NoraLife Hospital</h1>
    <h2>Dedicated to your health and well-being</h2>
    <h3><strong>Compassion, Innovation & Excellence</strong></h3>
    <p>Since our foundation in 1945, we have built a reputation for regional leadership in medical excellence and innovation, based on a simple philosophy: that improving the health of our community should be driven by passion as well as compassion.</p>
    <p>We offer a range of spacious modern rooms and are equipped with state-of-the-art critical care units. At NoraLife, the best consultants, specialists, and employees are dedicated to providing exceptional clinical outcomes and the utmost customer satisfaction.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
